cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

This paper is about a competition focused on scene text detection, recognition, and spotting, which are all related to computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, since the paper also discusses evaluation metrics and participants' methods, it could also fit into cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.LG (Machine Learning), or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
